  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study was to evaluate the effects of 12 weeks' increased daily physical
      activity versus diet restriction on regional fat distribution, insulin sensitivity and
      adipokines including retinol binding protein-4 (RBP-4), leptin, adiponectin, and a new
      marker, adiponectin to leptin ratio (AL ratio), in type 2 diabetic women.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
